body_html: At the time those issues did arise also 1.0.1 was on PYPI (before March 24) which now contains 1.1rc2 so it will probably only affect those following the Anaconda and virtualenv instructions that point to install with the official 1.0.1 binary. That may help narrow down the possible affected users
